==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Furbelow
<hw>Fur"be*low</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Prov. F.
<ets>farbala</ets>, equiv. to F. <ets>falbala</ets>, It.
<ets>falbal⟦agrave⟧</ets>.]</ety> <def>A plaited or gathered flounce on
a woman's garment.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Furbelow</ent>⟦br⟧

